<h1>Welcome to Battleships</h1>

<h3>Instructions (2 players required):</h3>
<p>Both players place their ships on the defensive grid according to the chart on the right. Whoever goes first, calls out a position. <i>For example, G-6.</i> This will result in either a hit or miss. If a player scores a hit, the player goes again. Once a player has sunk all the opponent's ships, the player wins.<div class="start"><button class="btn btn-danger">START</button></div></p>
